            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1680047543937-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low until very gently bubbling and cook, covered, for 15 min</p><p>After 15 min, remove the pot from the heat and keep covered for a further 5 min – this is your <strong>sticky rice</strong></p><p>Tip: Don't peek! Keep the lid on the whole time to get fluffy and sticky rice!</p><p>Once done, transfer the <strong>sticky</strong> <strong>rice </strong>to a plate and spread it out flat to help it cool down</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1680047548310-x200.jpg",
