        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the sushi rice is cooking, peel and finely chop the <strong>shallot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>and peel and grate the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p><p>Chop the <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p><p>Strip the <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p>",
